  m_Name: MilitaryRecord_07
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::JournalData
  id: 37
  title: "B\xE1o c\xE1o qu\xE2n \u0111\u1ED9i #7 \u2014 K\u1EBF ho\u1EA1ch tho\xE1t"
  category: 5
  content: "\u0110\u1EA1i \xFAy Reyes \u0111\xE2y. Ch\xFAng t\xF4i t\xECm th\u1EA5y
    m\u1ED9t chi\u1EBFc xe t\u1EA3i qu\xE2n s\u1EF1 c\xF2n nguy\xEAn v\u1EB9n \u1EDF
    tr\u1EA1m s\u1EEDa xe b\xEAn c\u1EA1nh khu d\xE2n c\u01B0. K\xEDp c\u1EE7a t\xF4i
    \u2014 4 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \u2014 \u0111\xE3 c\u1ED1 s\u1EEDa n\xF3 trong hai ng\xE0y.
    Nh\u01B0ng zombie nghe ti\u1EBFng m\xE1y v\xE0 k\xE9o \u0111\u1EBFn h\xE0ng ch\u1EE5c.
    Ch\u1EC9 c\xF2n t\xF4i v\xE0 Taylor. Taylor b\u1ECB c\u1EAFn h\xF4m qua. T\xF4i
    m\u1ED9t m\xECnh kh\xF4ng th\u1EC3 s\u1EEDa n\u1ED5i. N\u1EBFu ai \u0111\u1ECDc
    \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c n\xE0y: chi\u1EBFc xe v\u1EABn \u1EDF \u0111\xF3, ch\u1EC9
    thi\u1EBFu b\u1ED9 \u0111\u1EC1. T\xECm b\u1ED9 \u0111\u1EC1 \u1EDF kho ph\u1EE5
    t\xF9ng."
  image: {fileID: 0}
  voiceLog: {fileID: 0}
